{"tid":2048031,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【國際戰線】英美醫護方舟計劃，齊齊救醫護！","createTime":"2020-06-02T13:42:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T13:59:48.000Z","uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"58f7fb5e80561a2980ade8b17db52d261f3e9e19","tid":2048031,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T13:42:46.000Z","msg":"英美兩國因為林鄭政府促成嘅武漢肺炎轉口港，已經有上百嘅醫護殉職<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/healthcare-workers-who-died-with-the-coronavirus-2020-4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhealthcare-workers-who-died-with-the-coronavirus-2020-4&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgWlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=b64dba09\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.businessinsider.com/healthcare-workers-who-died-with-the-coronavirus-2020-4</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/apr/16/doctors-nurses-porters-volunteers-the-uk-health-workers-who-have-died-from-covid-19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2020%2Fapr%2F16%2Fdoctors-nurses-porters-volunteers-the-uk-health-workers-who-have-died-from-covid-19&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgWlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=f26e2c20\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/apr/16/doctors-nurses-porters-volunteers-the-uk-health-workers-who-have-died-from-covid-19</a><br />\n<blockquote>香港於 1 月 21 日出現首宗輸入的新型冠狀病毒確診個案，患者為武漢人，1 月在 21 日搭高鐵來港，在高鐵西九龍站被發現發燒，即時送院隔離。而同行家人沒有病徵，於 1 月 22 日已轉飛菲律賓馬尼拉。</blockquote><br />\n連武肺病人同行家屬都可以離境，成個無掩雞籠咁！<br />\n<br />\n既然林鄭要對香港罷工醫護秋後算帳<br />\n不如就由香港人遊說英美兩國為香港醫護提供方舟計劃<br />\n安排香港醫護移民<br />\n補充英美兩國本土醫護人手<br />\n掏空香港醫療體系<br />\n實行終極攬炒！<br />\n幫手推到醫管局員工陣線睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由工會出面一定最有牙力做遊說工作！！"},{"pid":"9323f08b35ece7854d0879df77f7b8d3ef3e0802","tid":2048031,"uid":27530,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T13:45:11.000Z","msg":"多此一舉，不嬲醫護人員係好容易就移民到去英美，係大家都唔想移民，真係寧願喺香港住都唔走，你就知移民其實係幾咁辛苦"},{"pid":"2b5feeca5509395e04a6ff46c5fb20a7f82d85d4","tid":2048031,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T13:45:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d7cceec79195356c6ee94370b9f9824f3ccc82c","tid":2048031,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9323f08b35ece7854d0879df77f7b8d3ef3e0802","tid":2048031,"uid":27530,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T13:45:11.000Z","msg":"多此一舉，不嬲醫護人員係好容易就移民到去英美，係大家都唔想移民，真係寧願喺香港住都唔走，你就知移民其實係幾咁辛苦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T13:50:39.000Z","msg":"大家都唔想移民？<br />\n你坐咗幾耐<br />\n好多醫護都諗緊走喎<br />\n如果由英美兩國聯手策劃<br />\n俾多D甜頭(例如安排住宿)<br />\n整多D配套設施<br />\n佢地就更有可能離開香港"},{"pid":"5c6ad82e7102b9dc2f845fc9bb2d7f8d3b508552","tid":2048031,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T13:54:24.000Z","msg":"罷工醫護已成condom?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bb38a56407b3bc9cb1c088069225ec2dd0ce5ed","tid":2048031,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T13:59:48.000Z","msg":"唔撚係掛<br />\n醫護咁辛苦又要對抗林鄭極權<br />\n又要打武肺<br />\n居然冇人理佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}